+
+List read-only inspection commands and any approved smoke commands.
+
+## Files Allowed
+
+List files that may be inspected.
+
+## Files Forbidden
+
+List files that must not be opened, staged, or changed.
+
+## Evidence
+
+Include command output, file references, CI state, and PR metadata.
+
+## Final Report
+
+Lead with verdict and findings, then include residual risk and next mission.
