+# Task
+
+## Goal
+
+Validate a PR before merge and preserve evidence.
+
+## Scope
+
+Name the PR number, branch, allowed files, and required owner approval.
+
+## Forbidden
+
+Do not merge without passing CI, smoke, scope review, court comment, and owner approval.
+
+## Commands
+
+List PR metadata, CI, smoke, ignore checks, and post-merge checks.
+
+## Files Allowed
+
+List files allowed in the PR.
+
+## Files Forbidden
+
+List generated data, secrets, local config, backups, and reports that must not be committed.
+
+## Evidence
+
+Include PR URL, CI URL or status, smoke output, merge commit, and final git status.
+
+## Final Report
+
+Return gate verdict, merge status, evidence, problems found, remaining risks, and next mission.
